            <title>[JDK-8319773] Avoid inflating monitors when installing hash codes for LM_LIGHTWEIGHT</title>
                <link>https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8319773</link>
                <project id="10100" key="JDK">JDK</project>
                    <description>LM_LIGHTWEIGHT only uses the lock bits for its locking. This leaves the hashCode bits free when a monitor is not inflated. So instead of inflating when installing the hashCode on a fast locked object it can simply use the hashCode bits in the markWord.</description>
